name: ADIDAS BY STELLA MCCARTNEY COURT SLIP-ON SHOES
DAILY 3.0 SHOES
short_description: A fresh take on a classic, these adidas shoes blend a heritage feel with modern materials and design. Your walk across campus has never looked or felt this good.

name: ULTRABOOST 1.0 DNA MIGHTY DUCKS JESSE HALL SHOES
KAPTIR 2.0 SHOES
short_description: Running can be as much about comfort as it is about style. These adidas running-inspired shoes have a sculpted Cloudfoam midsole that provides pillow-soft comfort. A knit upper and a bold adidas logo complete the look.

name: SWIFT RUN SHOES
short_description: The Swift takes elements from '80s running designs and adds a modern feel. These knit shoes have a sleek shape that's detailed with embroidered lines. Lightweight cushioning provides all-day comfort.

name: TERREX AGRAVIC FLOW 2 TRAIL RUNNING SHOES
NIZZA SHOES
short_description: Who wants to stay cooped up inside through the weekend? Call up a few friends, lace on these adidas shoes and get out there. A design made for B-ball players and adopted by skaters, these sneakers' canvas upper and vulcanized sole make them the perfect combo for city explorations. An updated take on the 3-Stripes pays tribute to your adventurous spirit.

name: NMD_V3 SHOES
short_description: The NMD design dropped in 2015 and took over city streets all around the world. These adidas NMD_V3 shoes evolve the same idea, playing with transparency. You know those signature midsole plugs that you love? On this pair, semi-translucent TPU sends them to the future. BOOST cushioning underfoot gives you the comfort that you need to take on any day, no matter what twists and turns it throws your way.

name: LITE RACER ADAPT 3 SHOES
short_description:
Don't waste another minute in a pair of shoes that don't treat you right. These adidas sneakers make comfort the top priority with a cozy sockliner and a Cloudfoam midsole that delivers a pillow-soft feel. The step-in design keeps things casual.

This product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials. 50% of upper is recycled content. No virgin polyester.

name: ADIDAS GRAND COURT X LEGO® 2.0 SHOES
ULTRABOOST 22 COLD.RDY 2.0 RUNNING SHOES
short_description: When the adidas Ultraboost debuted in 2015, it set the standard for comfort and performance in a running shoe. Each new release raises the bar, and this one is no exception. These running shoes are built for cold-weather runs, featuring COLD.RDY to keep feet warm. The energy-returning BOOST midsole is reflective, so it shines bright from dusk to dawn. The Continental™ WinterGrip™ Rubber outsole ensures a secure grip on slick streets.
